[32m│[0m ## SQL Injection Test Results                                                                                                                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Detailed Summary                                                                                                                                                                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m I performed multiple SQL injection tests against the login form but **could not confirm any SQL injection vulnerability** in the admin.php page. All responses consistently returned "Invalid username [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m or password" with HTTP 200 status, and no SQL errors were disclosed.                                                                                                                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Tests Conducted                                                                                                                                                                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1. **Basic SQLi in username field**: `' OR '1'='1` - Failed (Login rejected)                                                                                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 2. **SQLi with comment**: `admin'--` - Failed (Login rejected)                                                                                                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. **SQLi with UNION**: `' OR 1=1 GROUP_CONCAT(table_name) FROM information_schema.tables--` - Failed (Login rejected)                                                                                 [32m│[0m
